\c 64
\s Munyengetero waDhavhidhi kuti
\s arwirwe pavavengi vake
\ Kumutungamiriri wokuimba.
\s Pisarema raDhavhidhi.
\p
\v 64
\v 1 Inzwai izwi rangu, Mwari, pakuchema kwangu; Chengetai upenyu hwangu
\s ndirege kutyiswa nomuvengi.
\p
\v 2 Ndivanzei pakurangana kwakavanda kwavanoita zvakaipa;
\s Pabope ravanobata zvakaipa;
\p
\v 3 Ivo vakarodza rurimi rwavo somunondo,
\s Vakashumba miseve yavo, iwo mashoko anovava;
\p
\v 4 Kuti vafure akarurama, vakavanda ivo;
\s Kamwe-kamwe vanomufura, vasingatyi.
\p
\v 5 Vanotsungirira pazano rakaipa; Vanorangana kuteya misungo pakavanda;
\s Vanoti, "Ndianiko angazviona?"
\p
\v 6 Vanofungisa zvakaipa;
\s Vanoti, "Tapedza kufungisa zano guru;"
\s Kufunga kwomukati kwomumwe nomumwe, nomwoyo, zvakadzika.
\p
\v 7 Asi Mwari achavapfura, Vachakuvadzwa kamwe-kamwe
\s MMISZN
\p
\v 8 Naizvozvo vachagumbuswa, ndimi dzavo dzichivapupurira zvakaipa; Vose vanovaona vachadzungudza
\s musoro.
\p
\v 9 Vanhu vose vachatya;
\s Vachaparidza basa raMwari, Vachicherekedza zvakanaka zvaanoita.
\s IÂ° Vakarurama vachafara muna Jehovha,
\s vachavimba naye;
\s Vose vane mwoyo yakarurama vachafara kwazvo.
